data.description:
Nestled in Indian River Heights, this delightful well maintained 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom pool home offers a taste of classic Florida living. Kick back and enjoy your very own private in-ground pool, perfect for sunny days and outdoor get-togethers. Just a short drive from Highway 50, making Orlando and your favorite fast food spots easily accessible. As an added bonus, enjoy rocket launches from the comfort of your own backyard, making your everyday life a bit more exciting.. With plenty of parking as well, this home is your gateway to comfortable and convenient living. 

NEW AC 2018, Roof 2005 Zero Leaks INCLUDES: Samsung TRIO Fridge, Electric Stove, and Dishwasher Appliance Set. Washer and Dryer Set. Patio Flat Screen TV Entertainment Set with Home Speakers. Yard Sprinklers Work!
